works.description: After announcing the Cal Flame products at the HPBExpo in Utah, the world leader in stylish home resort products, Cal Spas, has added the FA890L lounger spa to its Family Series of hot tubs. Offering a private sanctuary from the stresses of the day, the new FA890L lounger spa promises the best in luxury hydrotherapy with its 90 massage therapy jets, which work on key stress areas.
